nodes.long_description:
내가 좋아하는 모든 이야기가 여기에! 디즈니+에서 디즈니, 픽사, 마블, 스타워즈, 내셔널지오그래픽, 훌루 브랜드의 인기 영화와 시리즈를 만나보세요. 명작부터 최신 영화, 단독 공개 오리지널 시리즈, 라이브 이벤트 등을 디즈니+에서 스트리밍해 보세요. 지금 2D로 시청 가능합니다.

디즈니+ 멤버십이 필요합니다. 19+ 구독 가능. Meta 계정은 만 10세 이상부터 이용 가능하며, 최신 버전의 Horizon OS가 설치되어 있어야 합니다.

디즈니+ 콘텐츠/서비스 문의: 
(전화) 080-822-1416
(온라인 채팅) https://help.disneyplus.com

디즈니+ 이용약관 및 기타 정책: https://disneyplus.com/legal

디즈니+ 멤버십 구독 필요. 19+ 구독 가능. 

디즈니+ 콘텐츠는 지역 내지 서비스 여부에 따라 달라질 수 있습니다. 
영상 화질 및 오디오는 인터넷 서비스, 기기 성능, 멤버십 유형 및 각 콘텐츠에 따라 달라질 수 있습니다.

Disney+ är tjänsten där du streamar dina favoritberättelser. Här finns älskade filmer och serier från bland annat Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars och National Geographic. Streama de senaste filmpremiärerna, exklusiva originalserier och efterlängtade sportevenemang – allt på Disney+. Tillgängligt att streama i 2D nu.

Disney+ est la destination pour vivre les plus grandes histoires. Retrouvez les univers Disney, Pixar, Star Wars, Marvel, Hulu, National Geographic et FX, et profitez ainsi de superproductions américaines, de nouvelles productions originales, de séries exclusives et du meilleur du cinéma français dans une seule destination ! nodes.long_description:
Disney+ is the streaming home of your favorite stories. With beloved movies and series from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, National Geographic, and more. Stream the latest movie releases, exclusive Original series, and highly anticipated matchups all in Disney+.

With a Disney+ subscription you can stream in 2D format: 
- Over 100 titles in 4K UHD and HDR.
- IMAX Enhanced, see the full scale and scope with IMAX's expanded aspect ratio. Available with certain Marvel and Pixar titles and accessible on all devices where Disney+ is supported.
- A curated selection of unlocked Hulu content in the Hulu hub within the Disney+ app.*
- A curated selection of live sports events, ESPN Originals, and studio programming in the ESPN hub within the Disney+ app*

For help with Disney+: http://help.disneyplus.com

For our Subscriber Agreement and other policies: https://disneyplus.com/legal/subscriber-agreement

Your US State Privacy Rights:  privacy.twdc.com/state

Do Not Sell or Share My Information: https://privacy.thewaltdisneycompany.com/en/dnssmpi/


*U.S. residents, 18+ only. A limited selection of content from Hulu and ESPN are now available to all Disney+ subscribers. To access the full ESPN on Disney+ and Hulu on Disney+ experience, you must bundle those services with your Disney+ subscription. 

Disney+ Subscription required. You must be 10+ to use Meta Quest and have the latest version of Horizon OS installed.

Disney+（ディズニープラス）は、ディズニーがグローバルで展開する定額制公式動画配信サービスです。ディズニー、ピクサー、マーベル、スター・ウォーズ、ナショナル ジオグラフィックの名作・話題作に加え、スターブランドとして大人が楽しめるドラマや映画が見放題でお楽しみいただけます。ここでしか見られないオリジナル作品も充実しており、毎月新しい作品が続々登場いたします。現在は、2Dでご視聴いただけます。

視聴にはDisney+のサブスクリプションが必要です。Metaアカウントは10歳以上が対象です。最新バージョンのHorizon OSをインストールしてください。

Disney+の詳細は、http://help.disneyplus.comをご覧ください。

Disney+利用規約、その他のポリシーは https://disneyplus.com/legal/をご確認ください。

Disney+ is the streaming home of your favorite stories. With beloved movies and series from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, National Geographic, and more. Stream the latest movie releases, exclusive Original series, and highly anticipated matchups all in Disney+.


With a Disney+ subscription you can experience:
- Over 100 titles in 4K UHD and HDR.
- IMAX Enhanced, see the full scale and scope with IMAX's expanded aspect ratio. Available with certain Marvel and Pixar titles and accessible on all devices where Disney+ is supported.
- A curated selection of unlocked Hulu content in the Hulu hub within the Disney+ app.*
- A curated selection of live sports events, ESPN Originals, and studio programming in the ESPN hub within the Disney+ app*


For help with Disney+: http://help.disneyplus.com


**For our Subscriber Agreement and other policies**: https://disneyplus.com/legal/subscriber-agreement


**Your US State Privacy Rights**:  privacy.twdc.com/state


**Do Not Sell or Share My Information**: https://privacy.thewaltdisneycompany.com/en/dnssmpi/


*U.S. residents, 18+ only. A limited selection of content from Hulu and ESPN are now available to all Disney+ subscribers. To access the full ESPN on Disney+ and Hulu on Disney+ experience, you must bundle those services with your Disney+ subscription. 


Disney+ Subscription required. You must be 10+ to use Meta Quest and have the latest version of Horizon OS installed.
